cache/generation/drafts/accessibility-highlight-overlay.md:102:`UpdateOverlay()` updates the overlay from the current accessibility highlight target. In a dali-ui application, treat this as the bridge point from your focused `Dali::Ui::View` coordination code into the overlay update path. The public signature accepts the active highlight target by reference.
cache/generation/drafts/accessibility-highlight-overlay.md:104:Use `HideOverlay()` when the app should remove the accessibility highlight, such as when focus leaves the active view area or when the accessibility focus state is cleared.
